Beauty Thulani Zibula bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na onye otu National Assembly of South Africa
Zibula bụ onye otu African National Congress
Zibula bụ onye omeiwu na-azọ ọkwa onye omeiwu maka African National Congress na ntuli aka 2019

Ọ bụ onye nke iri na isii na ndepụta ANC na KwaZulu-Natal. A họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omebe iwu mba dịka ANC meriri oche iri abụọ na anọ na mpaghara ahụ. Dị ka onye otu National Assembly, ọ bụ onye otu Standing Committee on Public Accounts.
Na 2019 Register of Members' Interest, Zibula kpughere na dị ka onyeisi oche nke Clothing Manufactory Chamber nke National Bargaining Council, ọ natara R13 935.48.
